OL,3,CFormer restaurateur guilty of rape,
OL,4,Csexual offences and assault
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of rape,
OL,7,Ftwo further sexual offences and three
OL,8,Fassault charges against two women.
OL,10,FGavin Neil Roberts, 44, denied all
OL,11,Fthose charges, although he pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to other two counts of grave
OL,13,Fand criminal assault against one of
OL,14,Fthe women.
OL,16,FThe jury came to their decision after
OL,17,Fthree hours of deliberation at
OL,18,FJersey's Royal Court.
