OL,3,CFormer restaurateur guilty of rape,
OL,4,Csexual offences and assault
OL,6,FThe women were both known to Mr
OL,7,FRoberts but made their allegations
OL,8,Fseparately.
OL,10,FHe was described by the prosecution as
OL,11,Fsomeone who could be charming and good
OL,12,Fcompany but was also a "convicted
OL,13,Ffraudster" with an "established
OL,14,Fhistory of violence against women".
OL,16,FReferring to the rape charge, the
OL,17,Fprosecution said that Mr Roberts "took
OL,18,Ffull advantage of her and used her for
OL,19,Fhis own sexual gratification".
