OL,3,CFormer restaurateur guilty of rape,
OL,4,Csexual offences and assault
OL,6,FThe defence argued the women were
OL,7,Feither lying or inconsistent in their
OL,8,Fstories.
OL,10,FThe court heard Mr Roberts turned to
OL,11,Fdrink to cope with the pressures of
OL,12,Frunning a business as the then-owner
OL,13,Fof Shinzo restaurant in St Aubin.
OL,15,FThe prosecution described how on two
OL,16,Foccasions, away from work, he argued
OL,17,Fwith a woman he knew and grabbed her
OL,18,Fby the throat, amounting to common
OL,19,Fassault.
