OL,6,FReferring to Mr Roberts, she said:
OL,7,F"When he was drinking he became
OL,8,Fpossessed. It was like something had
OL,9,Fjust changed in him."
OL,11,FOn another occasion, he raped a second
OL,12,Fwoman he knew and carried out two
OL,13,Fother sexual offences in a violent
OL,14,Fattack.
OL,16,FMr Roberts will be sentenced later
OL,17,Fthis year.
